{"tid":480312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"手淫當車資雙程證婦涉色誘兼盜財　的士司機坐懷不亂擒人","createTime":"2017-11-26T04:52:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-26T05:07:01.000Z","uid":89696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ce96117c3c10ed2f5e4f98a0c3b8da8b94a44ef7","tid":480312,"uid":89696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T04:52:10.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】兩名內地女子乘搭的士，疑為了優惠車資，竟願意替司機手淫及讓他摸胸。其中一女「坐言起行」，抓司機陽具，又自掀襯衫，坦露乳房。司機坐懷不亂，嚴詞拒色誘陷阱。司機叫兩女落車後才發現手提電話不知所終，在附近街頭截獲一人，她曾交出2,000多元要求司機放過她。<br />\n記者：戴國輝<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20110319/15089977\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20110319%2F15089977&d=pdfsOOv%2BpbPhoedP6gJH9%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=a6fdf94b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20110319%2F15089977&h=0907ad00\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20110319/15089977</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/leLqUk5IZ0M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FleLqUk5IZ0M&d=pdfsOOv%2BpbPhoedP6gJH9%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=e7a87d4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/leLqUk5IZ0M</a>"},{"pid":"c02590bfdce7c803bf877365c1e5dc537250e3d2","tid":480312,"uid":128223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T04:53:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c866cdf307a01ce4e81b938b69a51084e0810ec8","tid":480312,"uid":73804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T04:54:01.000Z","msg":"Fake taxi"},{"pid":"122cbbd571a70210caa47f9231dded9b9e50b327","tid":480312,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T04:58:39.000Z","msg":"有睇降魔的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f7d60bf7d3a7a8e90e812e6cb18255d27ce1c7","tid":480312,"uid":7420